Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:59.34,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可曾记得？ 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:09.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:19.38,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:23.74,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:30.42,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.28,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:42.55,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:49.33,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.62,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.15,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:03.50,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:13.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:22.02,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:26.78,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
